### ==========================================

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/test-id

### ==========================================

### TEST 15: DELETE USER WITH TENANT TOKEN

### ==========================================

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/test-id
Authorization: Bearer {{loginTenant.response.body.data.access_token}}

