### GET /users - GET USERS BY ROLE (STAFF ONLY)

### ==========================================

### TEST 18: GET USERS BY ROLE - STAFF (TENANTS)

### ==========================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/users?role=TENANT
Authorization: Bearer {{loginStaff.response.body.data.access_token}}

