### GET /users/:id - GET USER BY ID

### ==========================================

### TEST 24: GET USER BY ID - STAFF

### ==========================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{loginTenant.response.body.data.user.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginStaff.response.body.data.access_token}}

### ==========================================

### TEST 25: GET USER BY ID - TENANT OWN PROFILE

### ==========================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{loginTenant.response.body.data.user.id}}
