### PUT /users/:id - UPDATE USER

### ==========================================

### TEST 30: UPDATE USER BY TENANT - OWN PROFILE

### ==========================================

PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{loginTenant.response.body.data.user.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginTenant.response.body.data.access_token}}

{
"name": "Updated Tenant Name",
"phone": "0899998888"
}

